    "arcs": [
        22,
        28
    ],
    "desc": "UwU Polymorphic Payment Registry\n\nM-of-N threshold attestation registry. Validator nodes sign over\nrefId || contextHash || userAddress (96 bytes) via ed25519_bare.\nA ref can be consumed exactly once by the designated userAddress.\n\npayments box record layout (72 bytes):\n  [0..31]  contextHash  \u2013 sha256 of the authorised calldata\n  [32..63] userAddress  \u2013 entitled consumer; zero = proof-only (non-consumable)\n  [64..71] isSpent      \u2013 uint64 big-endian; 0 unspent / 1 consumed",
    "networks": {},
